\par \lquote Yeah, you can have a word,\rquote  said Harry savagely. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \ai\af39 \ltrch\fcs0 \i\f39\lang2057\langfe3081\langnp2057\insrsid15346133 \lquote Goodbye.\rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af39 \ltrch\fcs0 
