\par \lquote  \rquote Ow dare you!\rquote  shrieked Madame Maxime. Her voice exploded through the peaceful night air like a foghorn; behind him, Harry heard Fleur and Roger fall out of their rose bush. \lquote I \rquote 
ave nevair been more insulted in my life! \rquote Alf-giant? Moi? I \rquote ave \endash  I \rquote ave big bones!\rquote 
