re you going to do in Binns\rquote s class \endash  read again?\rquote 
\par Exempt from the end-of-term tests as a Triwizard champion, Harry had been sitting at the back of every exam class so far, looking up fresh hexes for the third task.
\par \lquote S\rquote pose so,\rquote  Harry said to Ron; but just then, Professor McGonagall came walking along the Gryffindor table towards him.
\par \lquote Potter, the champions are congregating in the chamber off the Hall after breakfast,\rquote  she said.
\par \lquote But the task\rquote s not \rquote til tonight!\rquote  said Harry, accidentally spilling scrambled eggs down his front, afraid he had mistaken the time.
