\par \lquote Hello, Hermione,\rquote  said Mrs Weasley, much more stiffly than usual.
\par \lquote Hello,\rquote  said Hermione, her smile faltering at the cold expres\-sion on Mrs Weasley\rquote s face.
\par Harry looked between them, then said, \lquote Mrs Weasley, you didn\rquote t believe that rubbish Rita Skeeter wrote in }{\rtlch\fcs1 \ai\af39 \ltrch\fcs0 \i\f39\lang2057\langfe3081\langnp2057\insrsid15346133 Witch Weekly, }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af39 \ltrch\fcs0 
