time. Forced him into a compartment of his own magical trunk. Took some of his hair and added it to the Potion. I drank it, I became Moody\rquote 
s double. I took his leg and his eye. I was ready to face Arthur Weasley when he arrived to sort out the Muggles who 
had heard a disturbance. I made the dustbins move around the yard. I told Arthur Weasley I had heard intruders in my yard, who had set the dustbins off. Then I packed up Moody\rquote 
s clothes and Dark detectors, put them in the trunk with Moody, and set off for Hogwarts. I kept him alive, under the Imperius curse. I wanted to be able to ques\-
tion him. To find out about his past, learn his habits, so that I could fool even Dumbledore. I also needed his hair to make the Polyjuice Potion. The other ingredients were 
easy. I stole Boomslang skin from the dungeons. When the Potions master found me in his office, I said I was under orders to search it.\rquote 
\par \lquote And what became of Wormtail after you attacked Moody?\rquote  said Dumbledore.
\par \lquote Wormtail returned to care for my master, in my father\rquote s house, and to keep watch over my father.\rquote 
\par \lquote But your father escaped,\rquote  said Dumbledore.
\par \lquote Yes. After a while he began to fight the Imperius curse just as I had done. There were periods where he knew what was happening. My master decided it was no l
onger safe for my father to leave the house. He forced him to send letters to the Ministry instead. He made him write and say he was ill. But Wormtail neglected his duty. He was not watchful enough. My father escaped. My master guessed that he was heading
 for Hogwarts. My father was going to tell Dumbledore everything, to confess. He was going to admit that he had smuggled me from Azkaban.
\par \lquote My master sent me word of my father\rquote s escape. He told me to stop him at all costs. So I waited and watched. I used the map I had taken from Harry Potter. The map that had almost ruined everything.\rquote 
\par \lquote Map?\rquote  said Dumbledore quickly. \lquote What map is this?\rquote 
\par \lquote Potter\rquote s map of Hogwarts. Potter saw me on it. Potter saw me stealing more ingredients for the Polyjuice Potion from Snape\rquote 
s office one night. He thought I was my father as we have the same first name. I took the map from Potter that night. I told him my father hated Dark wizards. Potter believed my father was after Snape.
\par \lquote For a week I waited for my father to arrive at Hogwar
ts. At last, one evening, the map showed my father entering the grounds. I pulled on my Invisibility Cloak, and went down to meet him. He was walking around the edge of the Forest. Then Potter came, and Krum. I waited. I could not hurt Potter, my master n
eeded him. Potter ran to get Dumbledore. I Stunned Krum. I killed my father.\rquote 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \ai\af39 \ltrch\fcs0 \i\f39\lang2057\langfe3081\langnp2057\insrsid15346133 \lquote Noooo!\rquote  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af39 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\lang2057\langfe3081\langnp2057\insrsid15346133 wailed Winky. \lquote 
Master Barty, Master Barty, what is you saying?\rquote 
\par \lquote You killed your father,\rquote  Dumbledore said, in the same soft voice. \lquote What did you do with the body?\rquote 
\par \lquote Carri
ed it into the Forest. Covered it with the Invisibility Cloak. I had the map with me. I watched Potter run into the castle. He met Snape. Dumbledore joined them. I watched Potter bringing Dumbledore out of the castle. I walked back out of the Forest, doub
led round behind them, went to meet them. I told Dumbledore Snape had told me where to come.
\par \lquote Dumbledore told me to go and look for my father. I went back to my father\rquote s body. Watched the map. When everyone was gone, I Transfigured my father\rquote s body. He beca
me a bone ... I buried it, while wearing the Invisibility Cloak, in the freshly dug earth in front of Hagrid\rquote s cabin.\rquote 
\par There was complete silence now, except for Winky\rquote s continued sobs.
\par Then Dumbledore said, \lquote And tonight ...\rquote 
\par \lquote I offered to carry the Triwizard Cup into the maze before dinner,\rquote  whispered Barty Crouch. \lquote Turned it into a Portkey. My master\rquote s plan worked. He is returned to power and I will be honoured by him beyond the dreams of wizards.
\rquote 
\par The insane smile lit his features once more, and his head drooped onto his shoulder as Winky wailed and sobbed at his side.
