y, Crouch may have }{\rtlch\fcs1 \ai\af39 \ltrch\fcs0 \i\f39\lang2057\langfe3081\langnp2057\insrsid15346133 believed }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af39 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\lang2057\langfe3081\langnp2057\insrsid15346133 himself to be acting upon You-Know-Who\rquote 
s orders \endash  but to take the word of a lunatic like that, Dumbledore ...\rquote 
