\par Fudge reddened slightly, but a defiant and obstinate look came over his face.
\par \lquote And if I have?\rquote  he said, looking at Dumbledore. \lquote If I have discovered that you\rquote ve been keeping certain facts about the boy very quiet? A Parselmouth, eh? And having funny turns all over the place \endash \rquote 
