\par \lquote You admit that he has been having these pains, then?\rquote  said Fudge quickly. \lquote Headaches? Nightmares? Possibly \endash  hallucina\-tions?\rquote 
\par \lquote Listen to me, Cornelius,\rquote  said Dumbledore, taking a step towards Fudge, and once again he seemed to radiate that inde\-finable sense of power that Harry had felt after Dumbledore had Stunned young Crouch. \lquote 
