\par Snape made a sudden movement, but as Harry looked at him, Snape\rquote s eyes flew back to Fudge.
\par \lquote Malfoy was cleared!\rquote  said Fudge, visibly affronted. \lquote A very old family \endash  donations to excellent causes \endash \rquote 
\par \lquote Macnair!\rquote  Harry continued.
\par \lquote Also cleared! Now working for the Ministry!\rquote 
\par \lquote Avery \endash  Nott \endash  Crabbe \endash  Goyle \endash \rquote 
