\endash  the boy was full of some crackpot story at the end of last year, too \endash  his tales are getting taller, and you\rquote re still swallowing them \endash  the boy can talk to snakes, Dumbledore, and you still think he\rquote s trustworthy?
\rquote 
\par \lquote You fool!\rquote  Professor McGonagall cried. \lquote Cedric Diggory! Mr Crouch! These deaths were not the random work of a lunatic!\rquote 
\par \lquote I see no evidence to the contrary!\rquote  shouted Fudge, now matching her anger, his face purpling. \lquote It seems to me that you are all determined to start a panic that will destabilise every\-
thing we have worked for these last thirteen years!\rquote 
