rn, but what they grow to be! Your Dementor has just destroyed the last remaining member of a pure-blood family as old as any \endash  and see what that man chose to make of his life! I tell you now \endash  take the steps I have sug\-
gested, and you will be remembered, in office or out, as one of the bravest and greatest Ministers for Magic we have ever known. Fail to act \endash 
