antly, at his side. This Mark has been grow\-ing clearer all year. Karkaroff\rquote s, too. Why do you think Karkaroff fled tonight? We both felt the Mark burn. We both knew he had returned. Karkaroff fears the Dark Lord\rquote 
s vengeance. He betrayed too many of his fellow Death Eaters to be sure of a welcome back into the fold.\rquote 
