\par \lquote Your winnings,\rquote  he said shortly, taking a large bag of gold out of his pocket, and dropping it onto Harry\rquote s bedside table. \lquote One thousand Galleons. There should have been a presenta\-tion ceremony, but in the circumstances ...
\rquote 
\par He crammed his bowler hat onto his head, and walked out of the room, slamming the door behind him. The moment he had disappeared, Dumbledore turned to look at the group around Harry\rquote s bed.
\par \lquote There is work to be done,\rquote  he said. \lquote Molly ... am I right in thinking that I can count on you and Arthur?\rquote 
